o claims a drug for DOGS cured him of 'head-to-toe' cancer is tumor-free two years after doctors gave him three months to live<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/health/article-6965325/Oklahoma-grandfather-claims-drug-DOGS-cured-cancer-tumor-free.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fhealth%2Farticle-6965325%2FOklahoma-grandfather-claims-drug-DOGS-cured-cancer-tumor-free.html&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9WsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=49fb3210\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/health/article-6965325/Oklahoma-grandfather-claims-drug-DOGS-cured-cancer-tumor-free.html</a><br />\n<br />\nDaily Mail quote 既source<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.koco.com/article/edmond-man-claims-cheap-drug-for-dogs-cured-his-cancer/27276538\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koco.com%2Farticle%2Fedmond-man-claims-cheap-drug-for-dogs-cured-his-cancer%2F27276538&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9WsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=70a89100\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.koco.com/article/edmond-man-claims-cheap-drug-for-dogs-cured-his-cancer/27276538</a><br />\n裡面有講佢有同時參與其他治療，但得佢一個可以成功治療癌症<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">He was also taking an experimental cancer-fighting drug. But Tippens says out of the 1,100 patients on that clinical trial, he was the only one cleared of cancer.</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n呢度有比較詳細既資料可以參考，有埋reference可以睇 (太長未睇)<br />\n<br />\nMebendazole: A Cancer Fighting Drug We Find at the Supermarket<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cancertreatmentsresearch.com/the-over-the-counter-drug-mebendazole-acts-like-chemotherapy-but-with-virtually-no-side-effects/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cancertreatmentsresearch.com%2Fthe-over-the-counter-drug-mebendazole-acts-like-chemotherapy-but-with-virtually-no-side-effects%2F&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9WsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=9a6d10a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cancertreatmentsresearch.com/the-over-the-counter-drug-mebendazole-acts-like-chemotherapy-but-with-virtually-no-side-effects/</a><br />\n<br />\nA Drug Made for Animals and Taken by Humans to Treat Cancer: Fenbendazole<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cancertreatmentsresearch.com/fenbendazole/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cancertreatmentsresearch.com%2Ffenbendazole%2F&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9WsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=13a22cf3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cancertreatmentsresearch.com/fenbendazole/</a>"},{"pid":"9f26ce29bb114786bafee6b46b5ca6c1b9e1f90a","tid":1130331,"uid":18844,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:52:26.000Z","msg":"故事中的人食的狗藥叫「Fenbendazole 」<br />\n<br />\nscientific report article<br />\nArticle | OPEN | Published: 09 August 2018<br />\n<br />\nFenbendazole acts as a moderate microtubule destabilizing agent and causes cancer cell death by modulating multiple cellular pathways<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41598-018-30158-6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41598-018-30158-6&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9WsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=99bf17ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41598-018-30158-6</a><br />\n<br />\n係有啲根據的~"},{"pid":"8c9e7e384276168d2a6d24db307ade70d570fb0b","tid":1130331,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:55:20.000Z","msg":"去金魚街入定貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1367b022b31ab8be23b789bfb44c04825dde0227","tid":1130331,"uid":148332,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"37b640112a397f1875a9447bf658db8b676979f0","tid":1130331,"uid":60860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T07:39:58.000Z","msg":"有幾多個末期夠膽咁樣試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔係人人適用就係咁先<br />\n雖然用傳統療法都未必吊到一年命